    "twitter": null,
    "tag_list": "ux, web-development, community, web-standards, webdev, javascript, html5, css3, protagonize, taunt-media, entrepreneur, consultant",
    "overview": "<p>Nick Bouton is an award-winning user experience developer and online community architect based in Vancouver, BC, Canada. He has over 14 years of experience in software and web application design and development, and is passionate about creating and growing online communities.</p>\n\n<p>During his 3+ years at the Habañero Consulting Group, Nick was responsible for front-end development of web solutions, which included interaction and interface design and development, establishing look and feel, and ensuring usability. Now, as dynamic, independent developer, Nick has extensive experience developing rich internet applications and mobile web applications. He works primarily with HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, jQuery, various front-end MVVM frameworks (Kendo, Knockout.js), Microsoft ASP.NET / .NET MVC 4, Microsoft SharePoint 2010, Telerik Sitefinity, as well as various open source platforms.</p>\n\n<p>Nick now operates Taunt Media (http://www.tauntmedia.com), a consultancy that sponsors, develops, and nurtures several community-driven collaborative website properties including Protagonize (http://www.protagonize.com), a collaborative fiction-writing community of over 21,000 authors.</p>\n\n<p>Nick majored in Computer Science at UBC, and studied Java development at BCIT. Prior to beginning work at Habañero, he held a variety of positions including as development lead for OpenRoad Communications’ enterprise 2.0 intranet, ThoughtFarmer; as a software engineer at Versatile Mobile Systems, and as technical lead for Tribal DDB Canada in Vancouver.</p>\n\n<p>Nick recently founded the Vancouver Community Experience Group (http://www.vancx.com) and is also an active member of several other professional associations including the Interaction Design Association (IxDA), Vancouver User Experience Group (VanUE) and the Vancouver JavaScript Developers group (VanJS).</p>",
    "image": "http://crunchbase.com/assets/images/resized/0022/7421/227421v2-max-150x150.jpg",
