    "permalink": "christopher-da-sie",
    "twitter": "chrisdasie",
    "tag_list": null,
    "overview": "<p>Christopher Da Sie is a passionate User Experience Designer. He crafts beautiful sites that allow users to navigate web content in a pleasant way.</p>\n\n<p>He specializes in responsive front-end design work. But often times, he finds himself in the role of Front-End Developer working in languages like HTML, CSS and WordPress. This leads to the creation of Wirefy, a style agnostic wireframe tool focused on content and usability. By focusing on content, he is able to deliver strategic designs that displays large quantities of information in a clear, simple way with aesthetics that create a beautiful, emotional web experience.</p>\n\n<p>He started every project by evaluating the strategy and messages that the client wants to provide to their users. He looks for the best strategies of providing large quantities of information in a clear, simple way with aesthetics that create an emotional connective web experience. He believes in strong typography and solid color palates to help create this emotional connection. </p>",
