    "overview": "<p>Andy Crum is the Front-End Web Developer / Designer at Quartzy.</p>\n\n<p>Andy joined Quartzy in the fall of 2011 and leads Quartzy&#8217;s design and front-end development efforts. </p>\n\n<p>He comes from a diverse technological background, which includes time in Information Technology at Pfizer and Research and Development at Fujifilm. On a typical day at Quartzy, you may find him designing an interface mockup, creating an ad or identity piece, or knee-deep in HTML, CSS, Javascript, and PHP code. </p>\n\n<p>He is passionate about designing elegant solutions for complex problems.</p>",
